Diana drives



We began our vacation Saturday afternoon by driving up 101 to the Madonna Inn,
a hotel in San Luis Obispo famous for its theme-house rooms.
Taken Saturday, June 23, 2001, 03:42:27pm.  Original image size: 1600x1200, 1061kb
